## Header Component

Header 컴포넌트를 생성합니다.

```javascript title="src/components/Header/index.js"
import React from "react";

const Header = () => {
  return <div>This is header</div>;
};

export default Header;
```

<button
  onClick={() => {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(`
import React from "react";
const Header = () => {
  return <div>This is header</div>;
};

export default Header;
`);
    document.getElementById("copy1").textContent = "✔️ copied";
    setTimeout(() => {
      document.getElementById("copy1").textContent = "";
    }, 2000);
